'''内莉亚·亨特·拜登'''（{{lang-en|Neilia Hunter Biden}}，{{bd|1942年|7月28日|1972年|12月18日}}）；婚前姓'''亨特'''（{{lang-en|Hunter}}），是一位教师。她的丈夫是現任美国总统、第47任副總統[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]。1972年，她與自己的幼女在一場車禍中身亡。她的兩個兒子[[博·拜登|博·拜登]]和[[亨特·拜登|亨特·拜登]]在這場車禍中身受重傷。

== 早年及教育经历 == 
内莉亚·亨特於1942年7月28日生于[[纽约州|纽约州]][[斯卡尼阿特勒斯|斯卡尼阿特勒斯]]<ref name="NHJBNJ">{{cite news |date=1966-03-29 |title=Neilia Hunter to marry J. R. Biden |work=The News Journal |location=Wilmington, Del. |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/30963055/the-news-journal/ |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728054744/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/30963055/the-news-journal/ }}</ref>。中学就读于[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]（Penn Hall），活跃于学校的[[法语|法语]]俱乐部、[[曲棍球|曲棍球]]队、[[游泳|游泳]]队及{{tsl|en|student council|學生會}}<ref name="JBM6Y">{{cite news |title=Joe Biden Was Married To His First Wife, Neilia Hunter, For Only 6 Years |url=https://www.womenshealthmag.com/relationships/a32440131/joe-biden-first-wife-neila-hunter/ |work=Women's Health |date=2020-05-13 |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111063450/https://www.womenshealthmag.com/relationships/a32440131/joe-biden-first-wife-neila-hunter/ }}</ref>。随后就读于[[雪城大學|雪城大學]]，担任{{tsl|en|Syracuse City School District|雪城學區}}老师<ref name="NHJBNJ"/>，受前[[奧本_(紐約州)|奧本 (紐約州)]]市议员（Robert Hunter）提携<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rocheleau |first1=Kelly |title='A good, caring person': Former Auburn city councilor Robert Hunter remembered |date=2020-04-01 |url=https://auburnpub.com/news/local/a-good-caring-person-former-auburn-city-councilor-robert-hunter-remembered/article_ba25c123-e085-5fa3-8c22-7ebd001b4bb7.html |work=Auburn Citizen |location=Auburn, New York |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728054746/https://auburnpub.com/news/local/a-good-caring-person-former-auburn-city-councilor-robert-hunter-remembered/article_ba25c123-e085-5fa3-8c22-7ebd001b4bb7.html }}</ref>。

== 结婚 ==
內莉亞·亨特在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]][[拿骚_(巴哈马)|拿骚 (巴哈马)]]结识乔·拜登，当时喬·拜登在放[[春假|春假]]<ref name="OEJBNYR">{{cite news |last1=Osnos |first1=Evan |title=The Evolution of Joe Biden |url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/07/28/biden-agenda |work=The New Yorker |date=July 28, 2014 <!-- issue date--> |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814120718/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/07/28/biden-agenda }}</ref>。不久后，喬·拜登搬到雪城上[[法学院|法学院]]。两人于1966年8月27日结婚<ref name="JBM6Y" />。婚后，喬·拜登夫妇搬到[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[威尔明顿_(特拉华州)|威尔明顿 (特拉华州)]]，当时喬·拜登是当地{{le|特拉華州紐卡斯爾縣|New Castle County Council}}的议员。两人育有三个孩子：[[博·拜登|博·拜登]]、[[亨特·拜登|亨特·拜登]]和娜奥米·拜登<ref>{{cite news |author1=Sarika Jagtiani |author2=Meredith Newman |author3=Andrew Sharp |date=2019-09-25 |title=Hunter Biden: A brief bio of former Vice President Joe Biden's son |url=https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2019/09/25/hunter-biden-dealings-ukraine-his-personal-life/2439165001/ |work=The News Journal |location=Wilmington, Del. |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212065325/https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2019/09/25/hunter-biden-dealings-ukraine-his-personal-life/2439165001/ }}</ref>。随后喬·拜登参加竞选，争夺特拉华州参议员{{tsl|en|J. Caleb Boggs|J. 迦勒博格斯}}辞任所留下的悬空席位，外界称内莉亚·杭特是喬·拜登竞选团队的“大脑”<ref name="JBM6Y" />。

== 车祸身亡 ==
1972年12月18日，喬·拜登当选参议员不久后，内莉亚·杭特开车载三个孩子去买[[圣诞树|圣诞树]]<ref name="MJJBH">{{cite news |last1=McBride |first1=Jessica |title=How Did Joe Biden's First Wife, Neilia Hunter, Die? |url=https://heavy.com/news/2019/04/joe-biden-first-wife-die-death/ |work=Heavy.com |date=2019-04-25 |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224024423/https://heavy.com/news/2019/04/joe-biden-first-wife-die-death/ }}</ref>。她开车沿[[郝凱森_(特拉華州)|郝凱森 (特拉華州)]]（Valley Road）往西边行驶，在{{tsl|en|Delaware Route 7|特拉華州 7 號公路}}十字路口使与一辆北行的[[半掛式卡車|半掛式卡車]]相撞<ref name=biography>{{cite web|last=Ott|first=Tim|title=Joe Biden: The Heartbreaking Car Accident that Killed His Wife and Daughter|publisher=Biography.com|date=2020-09-28|url=https://www.biography.com/news/joe-biden-first-wife-daughter-car-accident-story|access-date=2020-10-28|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030022428/https://www.biography.com/news/joe-biden-first-wife-daughter-car-accident-story}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Hamilton |first1=Carl |title=Daughter of man in '72 Biden crash seeks apology from widowed Senator |url=https://www.newarkpostonline.com/news/local/daughter-of-man-in-72-biden-crash-seeks-apology-from-widowed-senator/article_6c9a477e-63be-561b-b771-1330b4cda02d.html |date=2008-10-30 |website=Newark Post |access-date=2021-01-22 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204160726/https://www.newarkpostonline.com/news/local/daughter-of-man-in-72-biden-crash-seeks-apology-from-widowed-senator/article_6c9a477e-63be-561b-b771-1330b4cda02d.html }}</ref>。随后她和三个孩子被送到{{tsl|en|Wilmington General Hospital|克里斯蒂安娜護理}}，她和娜奥米·拜登在抵达医院时已死亡，而两个儿子虽受重伤，但保住性命<ref name="MJJBH" /><ref name=biography/><ref>{{cite news |last1=Macon |first1=Alexandra |title=Joe and Jill Biden's Love Story Will Pull at Your Heartstrings |date=2016-11-17 |url=https://www.vogue.com/article/joe-jill-biden-love-story-pull-heartstrings |work=Vogue |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109055413/https://www.vogue.com/article/joe-jill-biden-love-story-pull-heartstrings }}</ref>。乔·拜登宣誓就任参议员时，他的两个儿子还躺在医院<ref name="JBM6Y" />。

== 影响 ==
在2015年[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]毕业典礼演讲中，喬·拜登提到他的亡妻：“如果不是那场致命的车祸，我可能还不知道我和孩子们的纽带是一份礼物。我照顾两个儿子，从中得到了救赎<ref>{{cite news |author=Lauren Holter |date=2015-10-07 |title=What Happened To Joe Biden's First Wife, Neilia, And Daughter Naomi? It's A Heartbreaking Story |url=https://www.bustle.com/p/what-happened-to-joe-bidens-first-wife-neilia-daughter-naomi-its-a-heartbreaking-story-6911491 |work=Bustle |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728054744/https://www.bustle.com/p/what-happened-to-joe-bidens-first-wife-neilia-daughter-naomi-its-a-heartbreaking-story-6911491 }}</ref>。”

威尔明顿郊区有一个名为内莉亚·亨特·拜登纪念公园（Neilia Hunter Biden Park）的非法人公园，用来纪念内莉亚·杭特<ref>{{cite web |title=Neilia Hunter Biden Park |url=https://foursquare.com/v/neilia-hunter-biden-park/4d5d705e9ac9a0931b6a7b94 |website=Foursquare City Guide |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728054744/https://foursquare.com/v/neilia-hunter-biden-park/4d5d705e9ac9a0931b6a7b94 }}</ref>。内莉亚·杭特父亲多年来在{{tsl|en|Cayuga Community College|卡尤加社區學院}}经营食堂业务，学校为了纪念她，每年为两名毕业生颁发内莉亚·亨特·拜登奖，一个颁给[[新闻学|新闻学]]学生，一个颁给[[英語文學|英語文學]]学生<ref>{{cite web |title=The Joe Biden Auburn met 48 years ago |url=https://auburnpub.com/news/local/ormie-king-the-joe-biden-auburn-met-48-years-ago/article_b714b01f-c806-5c6a-a46a-070ce87e1060.html |website=Auburn Pub |language=en |date=2020-08-23 |access-date=2021-01-22 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130165824/https://auburnpub.com/news/local/ormie-king-the-joe-biden-auburn-met-48-years-ago/article_b714b01f-c806-5c6a-a46a-070ce87e1060.html }}</ref>。

